CroisiEurope (Alsace Croisières until 1997), is an international river cruise company. It operates a fleet of river cruising vessels along the rivers of Europe, Russia, Mekong, Birmania, Africa, South America and United States.
The company also offers cruises on seas, like the Mediterranean Sea, the Baltic Sea, the Black sea…
CroisiEurope has offices and sales offices in Strasbourg, Lyon, Paris, Nice, Lausanne, United States…
